WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.640
To prove you’re not suspicious,

2
00:00:01.840 --> 00:00:02.500
got it?

3
00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:03.540
Don’t come closer,

4
00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:06.580
no, no, no!

5
00:00:07.060 --> 00:00:08.000
You’re not suspicious,

6
00:00:08.220 --> 00:00:09.660
but I don’t care if you are,

7
00:00:09.980 --> 00:00:10.980
you’re coming with me.

8
00:00:12.280 --> 00:00:14.840
Monster, beast!

9
00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:18.980
No, no, please, don’t!

10
00:00:21.720 --> 00:00:23.920
If you don’t say you like her,

11
00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:25.500
and don’t even dare to leave a mark,

12
00:00:25.880 --> 00:00:26.960
how can you call it love?

13
00:00:30.380 --> 00:00:32.620
Your girlfriend’s voice is nice,

14
00:00:32.620 --> 00:00:35.300
like a natural melody.

15
00:00:36.240 --> 00:00:37.380
Next time, if there’s a chance,

16
00:00:37.620 --> 00:00:38.820
let her sing for real.